column1: Daily Weather Observations for Warracknabeal, Victoria for March 2016
Prepared at 13:04 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW3082.201603
Most observations taken from Warracknabeal, but pressure from Horsham Airport.
Horsham Airport is several kilometres south of Warracknabeal, so the pressures will sometimes be markedly different.
Temperature, humidity, wind, cloud and rainfall observations are from Warracknabeal Museum {station 078077}
Pressure observations are from Horsham Aerodrome {station 079100}
